    "image_with_text_b6RWtx": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_pxVyLB": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "The Guarantee",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_GeV3tJ": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Now we know that this still leaves you to make a massive leap of faith. But remember that this is a completely non-invasive approach that requires you sleeping with an appliance in your mouth.  <br/><br/><strong>It costs just $100</strong>, and we fully refund your money within 90 days if after making a consistent effort you decide you are not satisfied with your experience. To demonstrate this we ask that you try to sleep with the appliance for a period of 30 days.  <br/><br/>Note that the guarantee only applies when purchasing the support package. If you buy just the appliance there is no guarantee as it is a 'do-it-yourself' approach.</p>",
            "text_style": "body",
            "text_size": "medium",
            "show_below_image": false
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
